If you have 8 spare minutes and looking for something to watch hit the link in my bio to view some fun moments from the past 10 days in Hawaii. Featuring a fun session at Haleiwa with @rissmoore10 & @caroline_markss  with a few incredible waves from @griffin_cola @crosbycola & @ethan_ewing . A fun and challenging Coco head hike, and some hilarious tennis moments with the Aussies. 
Enjoy 🙌

LP

Hey Guys, 

I've been spending my time in San Clemente lately where I've  utilised the @murfelectricbike program, endless amount of  waves  and delicious coffee's. Thanks for this  weeks question; What is your favourite  Coffee order? Hope this gives you an insight. 

Keep  sending  in  your questions and I  will try and give you  an answer in my future Mini-VLOG series. 

Stoked on having my new Hero 9 @gopro to capture the fun🤗

LP
